problem_statement:
Wrap FCNGradientBase

It looks like one important feature of `Minuit` that is not exposed by `iminuit` is the possibility for the user to compute gradients themselves (see http://root.cern.ch/root/html/ROOT__Minuit2__FCNGradientBase.html).

@piti118 Do you think it would be useful to add this? Any thoughts on how to expose this to the end user?

